meta_description: Adorable pink stripe organic cotton babygro with a hand-crocheted owl motif. Ethically sourced and machine washable. Perfect gift for little ones.
product_description: The Albetta Crochet Ollie Owl Babygro is the perfect gift for your little one. This adorable baby grow is made from soft, ethically sourced, pink striped organic cotton and features a meticulously hand-crocheted owl motif. The gorgeous and modern design makes this babygro a must-have for any stylish baby. This comfortable and adorable babygro is machine washable at 30°C for easy care. Give your little one the gift of comfort and style with this unique and charming babygro.
